{"tid":1361692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727唔可以再犧牲任何一位手足！！！","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:52:49.000Z","uid":207111,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d773c4fda6304e3a6c8059fb45d07ddacae62f32","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"好多人話光復元朗有危險<br />\n又有人話唔去唔得<br />\n衡量雙方既意見 <br />\n我個人建議 727當日應該要做到和理非既極致<br />\n遊行可以照去 <br />\n俾人打可以照還拖<br />\n但係一定唔好做額外野 如堵路 破壞 塗鴉等行為<br />\n裝備要帶齊 但只帶防守裝<br />\n遊行完夠鐘就走<br />\n唔好俾任何把柄或者理由俾黑警/黑社會開拖<br />\n<br />\n主要目的就係<br />\n我地唔可以再係呢啲副本戰場度失去任何一個人<br />\n拉下又幾十個 拉下又幾十個<br />\n遲啲返到去主線 就無人再衝嫁喇<br />\n<br />\n所以緊記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727要絕對和理非！一個都不能少！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b26c71336bdcdbaa2e9e8e375e760d485632004a","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4a9c88c5aa576db9157f84fb9f1ac26a8096b5b","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4a348dbdcb15029646babf345da8dc5eae2626a","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a066189b9febf0aaa2315fa250900b8834e39f3","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f979152e58eaa4b067ad62bf3668abfb03bd0929","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"41121d25982bfd4369e897be7f2bd500e7a22857","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f47df961ef41ab8f746c2af031f9627ac5b451cd","tid":1361692,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:52:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}